title: SUPERIOR SPIDER-MAN TEAM-UP 006 (2014) (Marvel) (digital-Empire)
description:
The Avengers, S.H.I.E.L.D. and the Mayor of New York are all disturbed to see that the Superior Spider-Man's new team consists of the former members of the Sinister Six. However, he's actually controlling them with his mind, and you just know that won't end well! Check it out.

THE SUPERIOR SIX CONTINUES!
Spider-Man has formed his own SUPERIOR super-hero team... out of the SINISTER SIX!
As Spider-Man deals with the challenges his new team poses, Lightmaster makes his move!
Can Spider-Man trust his new team, aka his greatest enemies, when a reformed Masters of Evil come calling?
